Later, when the user tried to continue the bug PR, Spark returned Memory Doctor diagnostics instead of continuing the bug packet.

Expected:
Spark should return:

• prerequisites 
• copyable Windows PowerShell commands 
• pass/fail checks 
• redaction rules 
• safe before/after proof guidance 

Actual:
Spark returned:

